snippet.textDisplay:
That awful nameste lyrics totally ruined an otherwise such a deep meaning song. Such potential. Wasted. 

@CokeStudio please do another version *without* those half cooked lyrics. Des Raj is such a jewel. Full of substance. Please capture his substance.

There's a difference in composing a silly Bollywood peppy track and a soulful rendition. This track tries to be both things at the same time and fails miserably at both.

Sorry for the harsh sounding words but really disappointed.
